		" 
			>
			<DIV></DIV>
<P>I just thought I would post this to give some ides, not everyone will agree but here was my list of pet toys when I was a younger bsty. All of these can be purchased in the bazaar usually by typing summoned in the search box and are running around 5 to 10pp each right now on luclin.</P>
<P>Hand of Ixiblat - was my weapon of choice because it procs with any pet over lvl 10. ( be aware when you are looking at required or recomended lvl's for pet items that your&nbsp;warder is not the same lvl as you and the listed lvl does in fact apply to the warders lvl.)</P>
<P>Crystal belt - adds I think 650 hps to your warder, there is also a smaller version that gives your pet 250 hps if this one is not availible.</P>
<P>Mask of Mardu - this gives your pet haste, I forget the exact amout atm though.</P>
<P>&nbsp;</P>
<P>Also be aware that the same hold true with warders as with all other pets, any pet you get after lvl 29 or 30 can dual weild so you will need 2 weapons if you are using 1h weapons or h2h weapons.</P>
<P>Hope this helps.</P>
								<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 120; overflow: hidden;">
								
							Zeddlar:<br>Iksar Beastlord of the 65th season, Luclin
